qually common.  See also  Alun ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Alan Cathcart 3rd Laird Cathcart was born in 1204, his father, William Cathcart 2nd Laird Cathcart, was 39 and his mother, Wife Of William Cathcart, was -26. He had at least 1 son with NN De Cathcart. He died in 1249, at the age of 45."},"et":{"1204–1249":"1204–1249","–Female":"Surnud","1235–Male":"1235–Surnud","1165–1234":"1165–1234","1230–Female":"1230–Surnud","1249":"1249","1204":"1204","1235":"1235","1234":"1234","ABT 1235":"umbes 1235","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","Of, Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Scotland":"Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1204–1249":"1204–1249","–Female":"Kuollut","1235–Male":"1235–Kuollut","1165–1234":"1165–1234","1230–Female":"1230–Kuollut","1249":"1249","1204":"1204","1235":"1235","1234":"1234","ABT 1235":"noin 1235","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","Of, Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Scotland":"Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1204–1249":"1204–1249","–Female":"Décédée","1235–Male":"1235–Décédé","1165–1234":"1165–1234","1230–Female":"1230–Décédée","1249":"1249","1204":"1204","1235":"1235","1234":"1234","ABT 1235":"environ 1235","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","Of, Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Scotland":"Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Alan Cathcart 3rd Laird Cathcart est né en 1204, son père, William Cathcart 2nd Laird Cathcart, avait 39 ans et sa mère, Wife Of William Cathcart, avait -26 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec NN De Cathcart. Il est décédé en 1249, à l’âge de 45 ans."},"de":{"1204–1249":"1204–1249","–Female":"Verstorben","1235–Male":"1235–Verstorben","1165–1234":"1165–1234","1230–Female":"1230–Verstorben","1249":"1249","1204":"1204","1235":"1235","1234":"1234","ABT 1235":"um 1235","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","Of, Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Scotland":"Cathcart, Renfrewshire, Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als Alan Cathcart 3rd Laird Cathcart 1204 geboren wurde, war sein Vater Willia